# content service

Module: `github.com/sedorofeevd/project-druzya/services/content`. Work from service root only.

## Layers

```
cmd/content/app/run.go       → DI
internal/app/api/content/    → gRPC/HTTP transport (one RPC per file)
internal/catalog/model/      → entities
internal/catalog/repository/ → postgres
internal/catalog/service/    → Service interface + use cases
```

## Dev

`make start` | `make run` | `make lint` | `make gen-proto`

HTTP `:8081`, gRPC `:9091`. See `AGENTS.md`.
